Consider the following system of linear equations:

\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
2x_1 + 4x_2 + 6x_3 &= 10 \\
3x_1 + 6x_2 + 9x_3 &= 15 \\
4x_1 + 8x_2 + 12x_3 &= 20 \\
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}

Write the system of equations in block matrix form and find the solution using block matrix operations.
